data.description: You can have the best lawn on the block with this gorgeous 3 bedroom 2 bathroom brick home that captivates you from the moment you see it. When you walk in the door, the care of the owners and the upgrades they have done throughout the home, include flooring, kitchen appliances and more, can be seen. Have your cup of morning Joe in the beautiful glass room patio addition while gazing out at your immaculately manicured backyard. Home is close to Interstate 95, Jacksonville International Airport, and Amazon. This home is just waiting to welcome its new owners with opened arms! Schedule your showing today!
